            From QuickBooks consulting to technology transformation, we provide integrated business solutions 
            that streamline operations, ensure compliance, and accelerate growth for small and medium businesses.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Enhanced CTAs -->
        <div class="text-center mb-20 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
